00:53:06.648 --> 00:53:07.658
Oke.

00:53:07.718 --> 00:53:09.288
(Tuan Shin: Scent Caf??, Gwangok-dong, Inyeong-si)

00:53:09.358 --> 00:53:11.758
Oke, terima kasih.

00:53:41.443 --> 00:53:42.543
Detektif Choi.

